    description: "Shot Scope LM1 ($199) vs Garmin R10 ($599) compared. Accuracy, features, subscription costs, and which is better for your budget and goals.",
    titleDisplay: 'Shot Scope LM1 vs Garmin R10 — Which Budget Monitor Wins?',
    excerpt: 'Shot Scope LM1 ($199) vs Garmin R10 ($599) — accuracy, features, subscription costs, and 3-year total cost compared.',
    bottomLine: 'Buy the <strong>LM1</strong> if you want accurate distances with zero ongoing costs. Buy the <strong>R10</strong> if you want simulator capability and full swing analytics.',
