    toc: ['Best Overall: Skechers GO GOLF Arch Fit', 'Best Budget: New Balance Breeze V2', 'Best Stability: FootJoy Superlites XP', 'What Causes Knee Pain in Golf Shoes', 'Insole Upgrades'],
