    intro: `The sticker price of a launch monitor is a lie. A $699 monitor with a $199/year subscription costs $1,296 over 3 years — more than a "premium" $999 monitor with no subscription. We did the math on every major launch monitor so you can see what you are really paying.`,
    toc: ['1-Year 3-Year 5-Year Ownership', 'Hidden Fees and Locked Features', 'Simulator Software Compatibility', 'Best Value at Each Budget'],
