    title: 'Trackman Alternatives',
    titleDisplay: '7 Trackman Alternatives That Don\'t Cost $25,000 (Tested)',
    description: '7 Trackman alternatives tested for accuracy, features, and value in 2026. From $199 to $15,000 — find Trackman-level data without the Trackman price.',
