    intro: `Trackman is the gold standard in launch monitors. Tour pros use it. Fitters use it. Teaching pros use it. But at $21,995+, it is priced for professionals, not weekend golfers. The good news: monitors costing 1/10th the price now deliver 90-95% of Trackman's accuracy. We tested seven alternatives to find the best one at each budget.`,
