    titleDisplay: 'MLM2PRO vs SkyTrak+ — $700 vs $3,000, Is It Worth 4x More?',
    description: 'Rapsodo MLM2PRO vs SkyTrak+ compared for accuracy, features, subscriptions, and total cost. We tested both to find which launch monitor is right for you.',
    excerpt: 'The MLM2PRO costs $700. The SkyTrak+ costs $3,000. Is the premium monitor really 4x better?',
    bottomLine: 'The SkyTrak+ is more accurate and has a better simulator experience, but over 3 years the total cost gap narrows to $2,300. The MLM2PRO is the smarter buy for most weekend golfers.',
    intro: `The Rapsodo MLM2PRO ($699) and SkyTrak+ ($2,995) sit at opposite ends of the launch monitor market. One costs 4x more than the other. The question every simulator buyer asks: is the SkyTrak+ actually 4x better, or is the MLM2PRO "good enough?" We tested both over 200 shots to find out.`,
    toc: ['Accuracy Head to Head', 'Features and Metrics', 'Subscription Costs', 'Simulator Experience', 'Indoor Setup', 'Our Verdict'],
    updateLog: [{ date: '2026-05-17', note: 'Initial publication — 200+ shots compared' }],
