    excerpt: 'Your grips are the only contact point with the club. Worn grips cost distance and accuracy. Here are the best options for every preference.',
    bottomLine: 'The Golf Pride MCC Plus4 is the best all-around grip. Cord upper half for rain, rubber lower half for feel, midsize lower hand for reduced tension.',
