    titleDisplay: 'How Many Clubs in a Golf Bag — Rules, Strategy, and What to Carry',
    description: 'How many clubs can you carry in a golf bag? The rules say 14 maximum. This guide covers the rules, recommended setups by handicap, and what to leave out.',
